creator: NIS a.d.
descriptionHtml:
"Gazprom card" application improves your everyday business, provides our expert support at all times and facilitates control and cost overview.


Become a user of our mobile application for corporate customers and take advantage of all of its benefits:

• Inform yourself about the prices of petroleum products and the supply of petrol stations directly from the mobile application
• Manage your fuel cards
• Keep up to date on your corporate cards
• Find the nearest gas stations with the help of the application
• Contact your responsible managers in our company easily and quickly
• Use quick reports designed to provide you with the most important information
• Be informed about newest promotions and news

Thank you for the comments and suggestions, we will use them to further enhance the application!
